### Variables
@baseUrl = {{baseUrl}}
@token = {{token}}

### Get all assets
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get a specific asset
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/asset_id_here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a new asset
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Company Vehicle",
  "type": "vehicle",
  "description": "Delivery truck",
  "purchaseDate": "2023-10-15",
  "purchasePrice": 25000,
  "currentValue": 22000,
  "serialNumber": "VEH123456789",
  "location": "Warehouse B"
}

### Update an asset
PUT {{baseUrl}}/assets/asset_id_here
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "currentValue": 21500,
  "location": "Garage A"
}

### Delete an asset
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/assets/asset_id_here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}